# Resume/CV

Add your resume PDF here.

## Filename

`salman-naveed-resume.pdf` (or update the filename in `config.js`)

## Tips

- Keep file size under 2MB
- Use a professional format
- Include contact information
- Keep it updated
- Consider creating multiple versions:
  - `resume-full.pdf` - Complete version
  - `resume-short.pdf` - One-page version
  - `cv-academic.pdf` - Academic CV

## Format Recommendations

- PDF format (best compatibility)
- Professional template
- Clear sections (Education, Experience, Skills, Projects)
- Consistent formatting
- Easy to read fonts

## Update Reference

If you change the filename, update `config.js`:

```javascript
features: {
    resume: {
        enabled: true,
        file: "assets/resume/your-resume-name.pdf"
    }
}
```
